### ============================================================
### Mall Cloud — Admin BFF 全量接口测试脚本
### 给前端开发用，覆盖所有增删改查接口
###
### 用法：IDEA 打开 → 先跑 Step1 → 再跑后面的
### ============================================================

@ADMIN = http://localhost:8030
@BFF = http://localhost:8090

### ============================================================
### Step 1：获取 Token
### ============================================================

# @name login
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/testLogin
Content-Type: application/json
{"username":"admin","password":"admin123"}


### ============================================================
### 1️⃣ 认证
### ============================================================

### 1.1 验证码（无需 Token）
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/getCode

### 1.2 当前用户信息
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/userInfo
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1.3 用户详情
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/userDetail
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1.4 菜单树
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1.5 在线用户
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/onlineUsers
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1.6 退出登录
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}


### ============================================================
### 2️⃣ 用户管理
### ============================================================

### 2.1 用户分页
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"entity":{},"page":{"pageNum":1,"pageSize":10}}

### 2.2 新增用户
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/insert
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"userName":"testuser","phone":"13800000001","email":"test@t.com","password":"123456","deptId":1,"jobId":1,"status":1}

### 2.3 修改用户
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"id":1,"email":"new@t.com","status":1}

### 2.4 删除用户
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"ids":[999]}

### 2.5 用户编辑数据
GET {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/1/edit-data
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 2.6 更新头像
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/updateAvatar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"userId":1,"avatar":"http://img.com/avatar.jpg"}

### 2.7 更新用户信息
POST {{BFF}}/admin/v1/user/updateUser
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
{"userId":1,"nickName":"管理员"}


